ENDLESS Legend Definitive Edition;ENDLESS Legend Definitive Edition;ENDLESS Legend Definitive Edition;;;OK;images\ENDLESS Legend Definitive Edition (2021).webp;;Amazon, Warez;Amplitude Studios;Sega;21/01/2021;"Endless Legend is the turn-based 4X fantasy strategy game from Amplitude Studios. Your home planet of Auriga is an inhospitable planet. As the leader of your people, it is your duty to protect and guide them... but you are not the only one trying to survive and thrive on this planet.

Will you be remembered as the explorer who unlocked the secrets of Auriga, the magnate who mastered the subtle arts of diplomacy and trade, or the warmonger whose legacy was written in blood? The choice is yours.

Endless Legend Definitive Edition, along with the base game, includes:

Endless Legend - Guardians
Who are these guardians? And more importantly, how will you harness their power?

Endless Legend - Shadows
The Forgotten are one of the major factions thought to be long gone. These masters of espionage, infiltration, and sabotage operate from the shadows.

Endless Legend - Echoes of Auriga
These seven new songs are here to further enhance your immersion in the world of Auriga.

Endless Legend - The Lost Tales
The minor factions are filled with characters whose stories remain to be told.

Endless Legend - Shifters
The Allayi faction has been on Auriga since before Endless. They are bound to Auriga, their bodies and minds reflecting the state of the planet, and they will do anything to defend it.

Endless Legend - Tempest
The oceans of Auriga still hold many mysteries, one of which is now revealed in the form of the Morgawr faction.

Endless Legend - Inferno
This faction thrives on volcanic terrain and will not rest until the rivers of Auriga are filled with lava.

Endless Legend - Symbiosis
The ancient Mykara faction joins the fray with one goal in mind: to restore balance to Auriga.

Endless Legend - Monstrous Tales
Dive in and discover ancient truths with these twenty new quests.";Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS), Indie;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.6d93b0e4-54dd-4046-9363-d72d877ef6fd
