The Elder Scrolls Online;The Elder Scrolls Online;The Elder Scrolls Online;;;OK;images\The Elder Scrolls Online (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;ZeniMax Online Studios;Bethesda Softworks;04/04/2014;"The Elder Scrolls Online is a massively multiplayer online role-playing game that was announced in May 2012. Developed by the team at ZeniMax Online Studios, The Elder Scrolls Online merges the unmatched exploration of rich worlds that the franchise is known for with the scale and social aspects of a massively multiplayer online role-playing game. 
 
