Galactic Civilizations III (Test branch);Galactic Civilizations III (Test branch);Galactic Civilizations III;;;OK;images\Galactic Civilizations III (Test branch) (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;Stardock;Stardock;27/03/2014;Galactic Civilizations III is the largest strategy sandbox ever made. Start with a single world and expand across the galaxy through diplomacy, trade, cultural hegemony or military conquest in this single-player or multiplayer 4X strategy game.;Strategy, Simulator;;epic_8931f79300d04c5889799bffc8ef70bd
Alien Isolation;Alien: Isolation;Alien Isolation;;videos\Alien Isolation (2014).mp4;OK;images\Alien Isolation (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store, Steam, Warez;The Creative Assembly;Sega, Feral Interactive;06/10/2014;"Discover the true meaning of fear in Alien: Isolation, a survival horror set in an atmosphere of constant dread and mortal danger. Fifteen years after the events of Alien™, Ellen Ripley's daughter, Amanda enters a desperate battle for survival, on a mission to unravel the truth behind her mother's disappearance.

As Amanda, you will navigate through an increasingly volatile world as you find yourself confronted on all sides by a panicked, desperate population and an unpredictable, ruthless Alien.

Underpowered and underprepared, you must scavenge resources, improvise solutions and use your wits, not just to succeed in your mission, but to simply stay alive.";Adventure;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/214490/24157/42c4e1443028b2f94c3ce58bbecde9ff062d3ddf/1750481001/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447363219;epic_8935bb3e1420443a9789fe01758039a5, steam_214490
Wizard of Legend;Wizard of Legend;Wizard of Legend;;;OK;images\Wizard of Legend (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;Contingent99;Contingent99, Humble Games;15/05/2018;Wizard of Legend is a no-nonsense, action-packed take on wizardry that emphasizes precise movements and smart comboing of spells in a rogue-like dungeon crawler that features over a hundred unique spells and relics!;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Arcade, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up;;epic_89443d0c5afa4ef586c72445c0399a8b
Alba - A Wildlife Adventure;Alba - A Wildlife Adventure;Alba - A Wildlife Adventure;;;OK;images\Alba - A Wildlife Adventure (2020).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;Ustwo Games;Plug In Digital, Ustwo Games;11/12/2020;Small actions can make a big difference. Join Alba, a young activist as she sets out to save a beautiful island and its wildlife.;Adventure, Indie;;epic_8a0173bbe3ac48ac903f5bc7277e7b4e
Insurmountable;Insurmountable;Insurmountable;;;OK;images\Insurmountable (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;ByteRockers' Games;ByteRockers' Games;29/04/2021;"Insurmountable is a strategic adventure game with roguelike elements, in which you have to overcome a dangerous randomly generated mountain. Confront the differing terrains as a lonely mountaineer and make your way through Ice, Snow and Stone. Use items to keep up your steadily sinking stats, while making your way up and down the insurmountable heights. The dynamic and ever-changing weather system, the day-night cycles, and numerous other events will make sure that you meet tough challenges on your journey to the top.

To live up to these challenges, you are able to improve your character. By earning experience points through events, you can choose skills to help you with certain playstyles. One of the serveral roguelike elements is permadeath, which forces you to try various strategies in your pursuit to summit the mountain.

The game focuses, on the one hand, on the decisions you make in a risky environment full of uncertainties, on the other hand, on evoking intense emotions people experience in such a harsh and savage environment.";Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;epic_8b556e7471ac46eda46445d93fa2e73f
