Turmoil;Turmoil;Turmoil;;;OK;images\Turmoil (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;Gamious;Playdigious, LTGames Global;02/06/2016;Turmoil is a simulation game set during the 19th century oil rush in North America. Get a taste of the rush and rivalry of the time as you earn your way to become a successful oil entrepreneur. As you make money digging up and selling oil, the town will grow along with you. Acquire more town shares than your competitors in a bid to become the new mayor.;Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;epic_9b1148db19dc457aa1adf9f21ac6f0ff
