InnerSpace;InnerSpace;InnerSpace;;;OK;images\InnerSpace (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;PolyKnight Games;Aspyr Media;16/01/2018;InnerSpace is an exploration flying game set in a world where physics are inverted. Take the role of an unnamed Cartographer to explore the Inverse, a collection of worlds where the Ancients once lived. Collect relics, and encounter each world's mythical demigod, in a quest to discover the secrets of the Inverse, its history, and its future.;Adventure, Indie, Simulator;;epic_Almond
