World of Goo;World of Goo;World of Goo;;;OK;images\World of Goo (2008).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;2D Boy;Microsoft Game Studios, Tomorrow Corporation, Brighter Minds, 2D Boy;13/10/2008;World of Goo is a multiple award winning physics based puzzle / construction game made entirely by two guys. Drag and drop living, squirming, talking, globs of goo to build structures, bridges, cannonballs, zeppelins, and giant tongues. The millions of Goo Balls that live in the beautiful World of Goo are curious to explore - but they don't know that they are in a game, or that they are extremely delicious. Congratulations, and good luck!;Strategy, Indie, Puzzle, Simulator;;epic_Anemone
Watch Dogs 2;Watch Dogs;Watch Dogs 2;;;OK;images\Watch Dogs 2 (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;26/05/2014;Set in Chicago, where a central network of computers connects everyone and everything, Watch Dogs explores the impact of technology within our society. Using the city as your weapon, you will embark on a personal mission to inflict your own brand of justice. Chicago's overarching network is known as the Central Operating System (ctOS), and it controls almost all of the city's technology and information - including key data on all of the city's residents.;Adventure, Shooter;;epic_Angelonia, epic_Jasper
