Tomb Raider GAME OF THE YEAR EDITION;Tomb Raider GAME OF THE YEAR EDITION;Tomb Raider GAME OF THE YEAR EDITION;;;OK;images\Tomb Raider GAME OF THE YEAR EDITION (2013).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;Crystal Dynamics;Square Enix, Crystal Dynamics, Feral Interactive;04/03/2013;Tomb Raider is a critically acclaimed action adventure that explores the intense and gritty origin story of Lara Croft and her ascent from a young woman to a hardened survivor. Armed only with raw instincts and the ability to push beyond the limits of human endurance, Lara must fight to unravel the dark history of a forgotten island to escape its relentless hold. The Game of the Year edition includes the Tomb of the Lost Adventurer, 6 single player outfits for Lara, 8 multiplayer maps, and 4 characters.;Adventure, Platform, Puzzle, Shooter;;epic_d6264d56f5ba434e91d4b0a0b056c83a
