DAEMON X MACHINA;DAEMON X MACHINA;DAEMON X MACHINA;;;OK;images\DAEMON X MACHINA (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store, Warez;Marvelous First Studio;Nintendo, Marvelous, XSEED Games;12/09/2019;"Daemon X Machina is a third-person action-shooter game in which players; represented by their avatars called Outers, pilot highly customizable mechs known as Arsenals on missions to suppress various mechanized foes. Choose and equip your Arsenal with a multitude of weapons, obtain more from downed enemy Arsenals, and swap them on the fly to suit your strategy in the face of ever-changing threats.";Adventure, Shooter, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up;;epic_f4f0d39fbb4640e0be62aa91d9eca87d
