<br>
</li><li> Command dozens of troop types. Interact with all the major D&D races. Deploy special forces. Send heroes on quests and build different types of structures and fortifications.
<br>
</li><li> Real-time combat occurs on a tactical screen with an overhead view.</li></ul>

