 <li class=""description__cool-point"">Explore never-before-seen parts of The Witcher world — Lyria, Rivia, Aedirn, Mahakam and Angren.</li>

<img src=""https://items.gog.com/thronebreaker_the%20_witcher_tales/image/explore.png"" width: 600px"">


 <li class=""description__cool-point"">Manage resources, recruit and develop units in your very own customizable war camp.</li>

<img src=""https://items.gog.com/thronebreaker_the%20_witcher_tales/image/manage.png"" width: 600px"">


