Seven Enhanced Edition;Seven: Enhanced Edition;Seven Enhanced Edition;;;OK;images\Seven Enhanced Edition (2017).webp;;GOG, Warez;Fool's Theory;IMGN.PRO;01/12/2017;"Seven: The Days Long Gone is an open-world, isometric role-playing game, in which you play as Teriel, a master thief sent on a mission that will shake the foundations of the Vetrall Empire. Free roam across the vibrant prison island of Peh, and choose whether to help or exploit its many citizens.

If there’s one place that Master Thief Teriel avoids at all costs, it’s the prison island of Peh. But when a daring heist takes an unexpected turn, Teriel finds himself shackled on an airship bound for the infamous island. To make matters worse, the daemon inside his head makes it very clear that the thief will never leave unless he does exactly what he’s told.

In Seven: The Days Long Gone you play as Teriel. You must use all of your cunning and clandestine skills to escape a web of deceit and betrayal, and ultimately survive Peh.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie;;gog_1276856962
Cave Story's Secret Santa;Cave Story's Secret Santa;Cave Story's Secret Santa;;;OK;images\Cave Storys Secret Santa (2021).webp;;GOG, Warez;Nicalis, Inc.;Nicalis, Inc.;10/12/2021;"Be the Mimiga Who Saved Christmas 
It's our holiday gift to you: Cave Story's Secret Santa, a new game you can 
download and play right now for FREE! It's a bite-sized side story of stealth 
and puzzle solving, with familiar characters, items and settings from Studio 
Pixel's fan-favorite indie adventure. 
After Balrog recovers the Christmas presents that Chaba stole from everyone
on The Island, the cowardly Mimiga named Santa must sneak into every 
home and return the missing packages. As he tiptoes past the beds of 
sleeping residents and avoids the vision cones of patrolling Gaudi, Santa 
finds useful items, eats delicious cookies and places the gifts under the 
Christmas trees where they belong.
Santa can bop the Gaudi to stun them temporarily, push or pull obstacles, 
turn light switches on and off, pry open ventilator shafts and more. But he'll 
have to watch out for hazards and avoid making any noises that might 
attract attention!
• Return gifts to 20 unique homes across three familiar zones 
• Find and consume delicious cookies
• Discover hidden passageways and secret surprises
• Enjoy retro graphics and sounds";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;gog_1278463559
