<br>
</li><li>Physics, water, and fire systems bring perilous environments of Lara's world alive, creating new deadly challenges and obstacles.
<br>
</li><li>Intuitive and fluid control system allows for seamless handling of any obstacle and interaction with dynamic surfaces.
<br>
