Showgunners;Showgunners;Showgunners;;;OK;;;GOG, Warez;;;;"In a dystopian future where corporations rule, a brutal reality show is the hottest entertainment property in town! You play as Scarlett Martillo, a contestant out for revenge. To win, you must navigate dangerous urban arenas packed with lethal traps and face off against hordes of heavily-armed psychopaths.
<br>
<br>
