&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Scavenge weapons, ammo and gadgets to raise your chance to survive&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Manage your inventory to make room for what you deem vital&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Different types of enemies will hunt you down each room of the facility&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;</li>
