Warhammer Underworlds Online;Warhammer Underworlds: Online;Warhammer Underworlds Online;;videos\Warhammer Underworlds Online.mp4;OK;images\Warhammer Underworlds Online (2020).webp;;Steam, Warez;Steel Sky Productions;Steel Sky Productions;28/01/2020;Warhammer Underworlds: Online offers high-stakes, turn-based strategy that pits mighty warbands against one another in an eternal battle for Glory in the realms of the Age of Sigmar. The streamlined fighter count of Warhammer Underworlds: Online makes it both easy to grasp and quick to play, while its dice-and-cards mechanics offer boundless strategic depth. Choose a warband, build your power and objective decks, roll the dice and carve a path to victory.;Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS);https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1022310/280290/e87ee70eabe3935a2ec990baf97a694811fb125e/1751177711/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1685030454;steam_1022310
Fantasy General II Invasion;Fantasy General II: Invasion;Fantasy General II Invasion;;videos\Fantasy General II Invasion.mp4;OK;images\Fantasy General II Invasion (2019).webp;;Steam, Warez;Owned by Gravity;Slitherine Ltd.;05/09/2019;"""Fantasy General II - Invasion is the reimagination of the strategy game classic from the 90s! Armies once again draw battle-lines on the war-torn land of Keldonia, and a new generation of commanders will test their bravery and tactics against each other. Fantasy wargaming is back! 
 
True to the tradition of the original game, Fantasy General II is all about turn-based battles. Lead over 75 different unique unit types, including powerful heroes. Take into consideration terrain, weapons and armour, magical effects, morale, and the balance of forces, make a plan, execute it, and vanquish your enemy, forging your reputation as a savage war-leader.""";Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS), Tactical, Card & Board Game;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1025440/240877/0f77c16b8906562cb7dd8d7cf398d7231df71909/1750607924/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1567171589;steam_1025440
