X-COM UFO Defense;X-COM: UFO Defense;X-COM UFO Defense;;;OK;images\X-COM UFO Defense (1998).webp;;Steam, Warez;Mythos Games;2K Games, MicroProse Software, Inc., Mediaquest;31/12/1998;"You are in control of X-COM: an organization formed by the world's governments to fight the ever-increasing alien menace.

